    <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/human-resources/MHR/850.html" title="MHR 850 - Coaching, Facilitation and Internal Consulting" class="courseListCourseLink"><span class="courseListCourseCode">MHR 850</span> - <span class="courseListCourseName">Coaching, Facilitation and Internal Consulting</span></a>
    
	
		<div class="courseListDescription">This course provides participants with an introduction to the knowledge, skills, and abilities needed to perform the roles of coaching, facilitating and internal consulting. It covers the planning for, implementation of, and evaluation of coaching, facilitating and internal consulting within the organization as well as the assessment and development of the interpersonal skills that are integral to these roles.</div>
	
	
		<div class="courseListLength"><span class="courseInfoLabels">Weekly Contact: </span><span class="courseInfoValues">Lecture: 3 hrs. </span></div>
	
	
		<div class="courseListWeight"><span class="courseInfoLabels">GPA weight: </span><span class="courseInfoValues">1.00</span></div>
	
	
		<div class="courseListUnits"><span class="courseInfoLabels">Billing Units: </span><span class="courseInfoValues">1</span></div>
	
    
